at the departments los alamos argonne sandia and savannah river 
sites went uncorrected for five years 
the gao report was requested by the house energy subcommittee on 
oversight and investigation and by sens pete domenici rnm and 
jeff bingaman dnm after a 10week strike by the contract 
security force at the los alamos national laboratory last year 
the congressional investigators said many guards hired as 
replacements during the strike did not have the required skills 
they also said an unannounced exercise conducted in april showed 
that 75 percent of the regular security force failed at one or more 
of the skills required 
