scotch pines green otherwise the trees would have a yellowish 
cast and gabrione said people expect a christmastree green 
color 
the paint also helps the tree retain moisture after its cut 
weiss couldnt say what chemicals are commonly used by christmas 
tree growers neither could laurie dornbush executive director of 
the michigan christmas tree association 
its something we want to look at dornbush said tuesday 
from her office in okemos 
shes interested in finding out what kind of chemical residues 
are left on trees by the time they wind up in living rooms or as 
garden mulch 
