there is no evidence of widespread hunger in 
the soviet union one of the worlds biggest grain growers and a 
food aid program shouldnt be necessary this year us officials 
say 
they produce an awful lot of meat and potatoes one analyst 
said 
germany already has pledged food aid to the soviets and 
