impact but was offset by the precipitous decline in the value of 
the ruble and the determination of farms and local officials to 
horde products for themselves or trade them directly for consumer 
goods 
as a result moscow which under the old system always enjoyed 
the best of what was available because it was the center of 
political power and influence is now in worse shape than many 
other areas 
